#, kde-format
msgid "Band-pass"
msgstr "Dvopolni pasovni filter"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_bandpass.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Apply a two-pole Butterworth band-pass filter with central frequency and "
"(3dB-point) band-width. The CSG option selects a constant skirt gain (peak "
"gain = Q) instead of the default: constant 0dB peak gain. The filter roll "
"off at 6dB per octave (20dB per decade). "
msgstr ""
"Uveljavite dvopolni pasovni filter s srednjo frekvenco in (3 dB-točko) "
"širino pasu. Možnost CSG izbere konstantno ojačitev krila (najvišja ojačitev "
"= Q) namesto privzetega: konstantne najvišje ojačitve 0 dB. Filter se "
"izklopi pri 6 dB na oktavo (20 dB na dekado). "

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_bandpass.xml:11
#, kde-format
msgid "Constant Skirt Gain"
msgstr "Konstantno ojačitev krila"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_bandreject.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgid "Band-Reject"
msgstr "Zavrnitveni pasovni filter"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_bandreject.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Apply a two-pole Butterworth band-reject filter with central frequency and "
"(3dB-point) band-width. The filter roll off at 6dB per octave (20dB per "
"decade)."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite dvopolni Butterworthov zavrnilni pasovni filter s centralno "
"frekvenco in širino pasu (3 dB-točka). Filter se izklopi pri 6 dB na oktavo "
"(20 dB na dekado)."

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_bass.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgid "Bass"
msgstr "Bas"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_bass.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Boost or cut the bass (lower) frequencies of the audio using a two-pole "
"shelving filter with a response similar to that of a standard hi-fi’s tone-"
"controls. This is also known as shelving equalisation (EQ)"
msgstr ""
"Ojačajte ali odrežite nizke (nižje) frekvence zvoka z uporabo dvopolnega "
"filtra police z odzivom, podobnim standardnim tonskim kontrolnikom hi-fi. To "
"je znano tudi kot izenačevanje polic (EQ)"

