#, kde-format
msgid "DC shift"
msgstr "Zamik DC"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_dcshift.xml:7
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Apply a DC shift to the audio.\n"
"This can be useful to remove a DC offset (caused perhaps by a hardware "
"problem in the recording chain) from the audio.\n"
"The effect of a DC offset is reduced headroom and hence volume. The astats "
"filter can be used to determine if a signal has a DC offset."
msgstr ""
"Za zvok uporabite zamik enosmernega toka (DC).\n"
"To je lahko koristno za odstranitev odmika enosmernega toka (ki ga morda "
"povzroča težava s strojno opremo v snemalni verigi) iz zvoka.\n"
"Učinek odmika enosmernega toka je zmanjšan rezervni prostor in s tem "
"glasnost. Filter Astats lahko uporabite za ugotavljanje, ali ima signal "
"odmik enosmernega toka."

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_dcshift.xml:11
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Set the DC shift, allowed range is [-1, 1]. It indicates the amount to shift "
"the audio."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi zamik DC, obseg dovoljenih vrednosti je [-1, 1]. Označuje, za koliko "
"se zvok zamakne."

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_dcshift.xml:14
#, kde-format
msgid "Limiter gain"
msgstr "Ojačitev omejevalnika"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_dcshift.xml:15
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Optional. It should have a value much less than 1 (e.g. 0.05 or 0.02) and is "
"used to prevent clipping."
msgstr ""
"Neobvezno. Vrednost mora biti veliko manjša od 1 (npr. 0,05 ali 0,02) in se "
"uporablja za preprečevanje porezovanja."

