#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_equalizer.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Apply two-pole peaking equalization (EQ) filter. With this filter, the "
"signal-level at and around a selected frequency can be increased or "
"decreased, whilst (unlike bandpass and bandreject filters) that at all other "
"frequencies is unchanged."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite dvopolni filter za izenačevanje vrhov (EQ). S tem filtrom se lahko "
"raven signala na in okoli izbrane frekvence poveča ali zmanjša, medtem ko "
"(za razliko od pasovnih in pasovno zavrnilnih filtrov) pri vseh drugih "
"frekvencah ostaja nespremenjena."

