#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_erosion.xml:6
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Apply erosion effect.<br>\n"
"    Simulates image erosion, an effect which will enlarge the darkest pixels "
"in the image by replacing the pixel by the local (3x3) minimum."
msgstr ""
"Uveljavi učinek erozije.<br>\n"
"    Simulira erozijo slike, učinek, ki bo povečal najtemnejše slikovne točke "
"na sliki tako, da bo slikovno točko zamenjal s krajevnim minimumom (3x3)."

