"Set the noise sigma constant.<br>\n"
"       \tThis sets denoising strength. Using very high sigma with low "
"overlap may give blocking artifacts."
msgstr ""
"Določite konstanto šuma, sigmo.<br>\n"
"       \tTo določa moč odstranjevanja šuma. Uporaba zelo visoke sigme z "
"nizkim prekrivanjem lahko povzroči bločne artefakte."

