msgid ""
"Set the luma threshold used as a coefficient<br>\n"
"            to determine whether a pixel should be blurred or not. A value "
"of 0 will filter all the image, positive values will filter flat areas, "
"negative values will filter edges."
msgstr ""
"Določite prag lume, uporabljen kot koeficient,<br>\n"
"            da ugotovite, ali naj bo slikovna točka zabrisana ali ne. "
"Vrednost 0 bo filtrirala vso sliko, pozitivne vrednosti bodo filtrirale "
"ploska območja, negativne vrednosti bodo filtrirale robove."

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_smartblur.xml:23
#, kde-format
msgid "Chroma radius"
msgstr "Polmer krome"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_smartblur.xml:25
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Set the chroma radius.<br>\n"
"            The value specifies the variance of the gaussian filter used to "
"blur the image (slower if larger). If not specified, it defaults to the "
"value set for <em>Luma radius</em>"
msgstr ""
"Določite polmer krome.<br>\n"
"            Vrednost določa varianco Gaussovega filtra, ki se uporablja za "
"zabrisanost slike (počasnejše, če je večja). Če ni določeno, ima privzeto "
"vrednost za <em>polmer lume</em>"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_smartblur.xml:28
#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_unsharp.xml:30
#, kde-format
msgid "Chroma strength"
msgstr "Jakost krome"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_smartblur.xml:30
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Set the chroma strength.<br>\n"
"            The value configures the blurring. A positive value will blur "
"the image, whereas a negative value will sharpen the image. If not "
"specified, it defaults to the value set for <em>Luma strength</em>."
msgstr ""
"Določite jakost krome.<br>\n"
"            Vrednost določa zabrisanost. Pozitivna vrednost bo zabrisala "
"sliko, medtem ko bo negativna vrednost izostrila sliko. Če ni določeno, ima "
"privzeto vrednost za <em>jakost lume</em>."

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_smartblur.xml:33
#, kde-format
msgid "Chroma threshold"
msgstr "Prag krome"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_smartblur.xml:35
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Set the chroma threshold used as a coefficient<br>\n"
"            to determine whether a pixel should be blurred or not. A value "
"of 0 will filter all the image, positive values will filter flat areas, "
"negative values will filter edges. If not specified, it defaults to the "
"value set for <em>Luma threshold</em>"
msgstr ""
"Nastavite prag krome, ki se uporablja kot koeficient<br>\n"
"            za odločitev, ali naj bo slikovna točka zabrisana ali ne. "
"Vrednost 0 bo filtrirala vso sliko, pozitivne vrednosti bodo filtrirale "
"ploska območja, negativne vrednosti bodo filtrirale robove. Če ni določeno, "
"ima privzeto vrednost, kot je nastavljena za <em>prag lume</em>"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_smartblur.xml:38
#, kde-format
msgid "Alpha radius"
msgstr "Polmer alfe"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_smartblur.xml:40
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Set the alpha radius.<br>\n"
"            The value specifies the variance of the gaussian filter used to "
"blur the image (slower if larger). If not specified, it defaults to the "
"value set for <em>Luma radius</em>"
msgstr ""
"Določite polmer alfe.<br>\n"
"            Vrednost določa varianco Gaussovega filtra, ki se uporablja za "
"zabrisanost slike (počasnejše, če je večja). Če ni določeno, ima privzeto "
"vrednos za <em>polmer lume</em>"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_smartblur.xml:43
#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_unsharp.xml:43
#, kde-format
msgid "Alpha strength"
msgstr "Jakost alfe"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_smartblur.xml:45
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Set the alpha strength.<br>\n"
"            The value configures the blurring. A positive value will blur "
"the image, whereas a negative value will sharpen the image. If not "
"specified, it defaults to the value set for <em>Luma strength</em>."
msgstr ""
"Določite jakost alfe.<br>\n"
"            Vrednost prilagodi zabrisanost. Pozitivna vrednost bo zabrisala "
"sliko, medtem ko bo negativna vrednost izostrila sliko. Če ni določeno, je "
"privzeto nastavljena na <em>jakost lume</em>."

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_smartblur.xml:50
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Set the alpha threshold used as a coefficient<br>\n"
"            to determine whether a pixel should be blurred or not. A value "
"of 0 will filter all the image, positive values will filter flat areas, "
"negative values will filter edges. If not specified, it defaults to the "
"value set for <em>Luma threshold</em>"
msgstr ""
"Nastavite prag alfe, ki se uporablja kot koeficient<br>\n"
"            za odločitev, ali naj bo slikovna točka zabrisana ali ne. "
"Vrednost 0 bo filtrirala vso sliko, pozitivne vrednosti bodo filtrirale "
"ploska območja, negativne vrednosti bodo filtrirale robove. Če ni določeno, "
"ima privzeto vrednost, kot je nastavljena za <em>prag lume</em>"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_sobel.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgid "Sobel with planes"
msgstr "Sobel z ravninami"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_sobel.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid "Apply sobel operator to input video stream."
msgstr "Uveljavite operatorje Sobel na vhodnem video toku."

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_sofalizer.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgid "SOFAlizer"
msgstr "SOFAlizator"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_sofalizer.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"SOFAlizer uses head-related transfer functions (HRTFs) to create virtual "
"loudspeakers around the user for binaural listening via headphones (audio "
"formats up to 9 channels supported). The HRTFs are stored in SOFA files (see "
"http://www.sofacoustics.org/ for a database). SOFAlizer is developed at the "
"Acoustics Research Institute (ARI) of the Austrian Academy of Sciences. "
msgstr ""
"SOFAlizer uporablja funkcije prenosa glede glave (HRTF) za ustvarjanje "
"virtualnih zvočnikov okoli uporabnika za binauralno poslušanje prek slušalk "
"(podprti zvočni formati do 9 kanalov). HRTF-ji so shranjeni v datotekah SOFA "
"(glejte http://www.sofacoustics.org/ za bazo podatkov). SOFAlizer je razvit "
"na akustičnem raziskovalnem inštitutu (ARI) avstrijske akademije znanosti."

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_sofalizer.xml:8
#, kde-format
msgid "SOFA file"
msgstr "Datoteka SOFA"

