#: data/effects/frei0r/mask_start_frei0r_alphaspot.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgid "Alpha Shapes (Mask)"
msgstr "Alfa v likih (maska)"

#: data/effects/frei0r/mask_start_frei0r_alphaspot.xml:5
#: data/effects/mask_start_frei0r_alphaspot.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This filter makes a snapshot of the frame before it draws simple shapes into "
"the alpha channel. Use it together with the mask_apply effect, that uses a "
"transition to composite the current frame's image over the snapshot. The "
"typical use case is to add effects in the following sequence: this effect, "
"zero or more effects, mask_apply."
msgstr ""
"Ta filter naredi posnetek sličice, preden nariše preproste like v alfa-"
"kanal. Uporabite ga skupaj z učinkom mask_apply, ki uporablja prehod za "
"sestavo slike trenutne sličice preko posnetka. Tipičen primer uporabe je "
"dodajanje učinkov v naslednjem zaporedju: ta učinek, nič ali več učinkov, "
"mask_apply."

#: data/effects/gain.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgctxt "Gain Effect Name"
msgid "Gain"
msgstr "Ojačitev"

#: data/effects/gain.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid "Adjust the audio volume without keyframes"
msgstr "Prilagodi glasnost brez ključnih sličic"

#: data/effects/gamma.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgctxt "Gamma Effect Name"
msgid "Gamma (keyframable)"
msgstr "Gama (s ključnimi točkami)"

#: data/effects/gamma.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid "Change gamma color value"
msgstr "Spremeni barvno vrednost game"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgid "GPS Graphic"
msgstr "Grafika GPS"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid "Overlay GPS-related graphics onto the video."
msgstr "Prikaže besedilo, povezano z GPS-jem, prek videoposnetka."

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:8 data/effects/gpstext.xml:12
#, kde-format
msgid "GPS File"
msgstr "Datoteka GPS"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:9
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The fullpath of file containing location (GPS) data. Supported extensions: ."
"gpx, .tcx."
msgstr ""
"Polna pot datoteke, ki vsebuje podatke o lokaciji (GPS). Podprte "
"razširitve: .gpx, .tcx."

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:12 data/effects/gpstext.xml:15
#, kde-format
msgid "Time offset in seconds"
msgstr "Časovni zamik v sekundah"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:14
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"An offset (in seconds) to be added to the video file to match it to the GPS "
"track.<br>\n"
"    \tMost of the time this will at least need to be set to the timezone "
"difference between the 2 files plus some seconds if the video recording "
"device isn't precisely set to correct time. GPS time is always exact and in "
"UTC. Use positive values if GPS is ahead of video and negative otherwise."
msgstr ""
"Zamik (v sekundah), ki bo dodan video datoteki, da se ujema s stezo GPS."
"<br>\n"
"    \tVečino časa bo to treba vsaj nastaviti na razliko v časovnem pasu med "
"datotekama in dodati nekaj sekund, če naprava za snemanje videoposnetkov ni "
"natančno nastavljena na pravilen čas. Čas GPS je vedno natančen in v UTC. "
"Uporabite pozitivne vrednosti, če je GPS pred videoposnetkom, v nasprotnem "
"primeru pa negativen."

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:17 data/effects/gpstext.xml:18
#, kde-format
msgid "Smoothing level"
msgstr "Raven glajenja"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:19
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"How many GPS points to smooth in order to eliminate GPS errors.<br>\n"
"    \tA value of 1 does not smooth locations, it only calculates the extra "
"fields (speed, distance, etc), it also interpolates missing values for heart "
"rate and altitude."
msgstr ""
"Koliko točk GPS je potrebno gladiti, da se odstranijo napake GPS?<br>\n"
"    \tVrednost 1 ne zgladi lokacij, izračuna le dodatna polja (hitrost, "
"razdalja itn.), interpolira tudi manjkajoče vrednosti za srčni utrip in "
"nadmorsko višino."

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:22
#, kde-format
msgid "Speed multiplier"
msgstr "Multiplikator hitrosti"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:24
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"If the video file is a timelapse (or slow motion), use this value to set the "
"speed up/slow down ratio.<br>\n"
"        Sample values: 30 for 30x timelapse, 0.25 for 4x slow motion footage."
msgstr ""
"Če je video datoteka posneta v časovnih presledkih (ali z upočasnjenim "
"gibanjem), uporabite to vrednost za nastavitev razmerje pohitritve/"
"upočasnitve.<br>\n"
"    \tVzorčne vrednosti: 30 za 30-kratne časovne presledke, 0,25 za 4-kratno "
"upočasnjene posnetke."

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:27
#, kde-format
msgid "Graph data source"
msgstr "Vir podatkov grafa"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:28
#, kde-format
msgid "What data from the GPS file is used for drawing"
msgstr "Kateri podatki iz datoteke GPS se uporabljajo za risanje"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:29
#, kde-format
msgid "GPS location/track,Altitude,Heart rate,Speed"
msgstr "GPS lokacija/sled,Nadmorska višina,Srčni utrip,Hitrost"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:40
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<b>Speedometer</b> is available for all data sources but recommended only "
"for speed; for the map type it represents the \"percentage done\" from "
"trimmed start - end).<br>\n"
"Note: for type 1 (zoom and center, aka \"follow the dot\"):<br>\n"
"* crop values are only valid as a percentage and only the bottom (resp left) "
"values\n"
"will be taken into consideration as both values (ie: bottom/top) will need "
"to be equal to\n"
"keep the dot centered)<br>\n"
"* if data source is not GPS location, the centering will only be done for "
"horizontal axis\n"
"(time), vertical axis crop will behave just like for the basic 2D map line "
"(it will statically keep\n"
"the same min/max limit allowing the Now dot to move up and down)."
msgstr ""
"<b>Merilnik hitrosti je na voljo za vse vire podatkov, vendar je "
"priporočljiv samo za hitrost; za vrsto zemljevida predstavlja »odstotek "
"opravljenega« od obrezanega začetka do konca).<br>\n"
"Opomba: za vrsto 1 (povečava in središče, znano tudi kot »sledi piki«):<br>\n"
"* vrednosti obrezovanja veljajo samo v odstotkih in samo spodnje (oziroma "
"leve) vrednosti\n"
"se bo upoštevalo, saj bosta morali biti obe vrednosti (tj. spodaj/zgoraj) "
"enaki\n"
"za ohrajanje pike na sredini)<br>\n"
"* če vir podatkov ni lokacija GPS, bo centriranje opravljeno samo za "
"vodoravno os\n"
"(čas), obrezovanje navpične osi se bo vedlo enako kot pri osnovni črti 2D-"
"zemljevida (statično bo\n"
"ohranilo enako min/maks omejitev, ki omogoča, da se pika zdaj premika "
"navzgor in navzdol)."

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:41
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Basic 2D map line (for location) or 1D graph per time (others),Zoom in onto "
"the map/graph centered on current location,Draw speedometer"
msgstr ""
"Osnovna črta 2D-zemljevida (za lokacijo) ali 1D-graf na čas (drugi),Povečaj "
"zemljevid/graf s središčem na trenutni lokaciji,Nariši merilnik hitrosti"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:44
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid "Trim start (%)"
msgstr "Obreži na začetku (%)"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:46
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"Trim data from the start of the GPS file (as a percentage of total). <br>\n"
"    \tNote: both <em>Trim start</em> and <em>Trim end</em> are computed from "
"the total file, so trimming 50% start and 50% end will result in trimming "
"the entire file."
msgstr ""
"Obreže podatke od začetka datoteke GPS (kot odstotek celote). <br>\n"
"    \tOpomba: tako<em>Obreži na začetku</em> kot <em>Obreži na koncu</em> "
"sta izračunana glede na celotno datoteko, tako da bo obrezovanje 50 % "
"začetka in 50 % konca povzročilo obrezovanje celotne datoteke."

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:49
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid "Trim end (%)"
msgstr "Obreži na koncu (%)"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:51
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"Trim data from the end of the gps file (as a percentage of total). <br>\n"
"    \tNote: both <em>Trim start</em> and <em>Trim end</em> are computed from "
"the total file, so trimming 50% start and 50% end will result in trimming "
"the entire file."
msgstr ""
"Obreže podatke od konca datoteke GPS (kot odstotek celote). <br>\n"
"    \tOpomba: tako<em>Obreži na začetku</em> kot <em>Obreži na koncu</em> "
"sta izračunana glede na celotno datoteko, tako da bo obrezovanje 50 % "
"začetka in 50 % konca povzročilo obrezovanje celotne datoteke."

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:54
#, kde-format
msgid "Crop mode horizontal"
msgstr "Vodoravni način obrezovanja"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:57
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Decides how to interpret the <em>Crop left</em> and <em>Crop right</em> "
"values.<br>\n"
"    \tNote: for the horizontal type, absolute values are the longitude (for "
"the location\n"
"source type) and time (in milliseconds since epoch) for the rest of the data "
"source types)"
msgstr ""
"Določa, kako tolmačiti vrednosti <em>Obreži levo</em> in <em>Obreži desno</"
"em>.<br>\n"
"    \tOpomba: za vodoravno vrsto so absolutne vrednosti zemljepisna dolžina "
"(za lokacijo\n"
"vrsta vira) in čas (v milisekundah od obdobja) za preostale vrste virov "
"podatkov)"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:58 data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:78
#, kde-format
msgid "Percentage from min..max,Absolute value"
msgstr "Odstotek od min..maks,Absolutna vrednost"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:61
#, kde-format
msgid "Crop left"
msgstr "Obreži levo"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:63
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"Crops data from the left side of the graph (effectively zooming in). <br>\n"
"    \tThe value is interpreted either as a percentage of total or an "
"absolute value depending on crop_mode_h. In percentage mode, the values are "
"not restricted to 0-100 to allow for \"zoom out\" behaviour (ie: cropping "
"-50 left will add an extra half of the total horizontal distance). Values "
"over 100 (in % mode) will effectively not display anything. If <em>Graph "
"Type</em> is set to <b>Speedometer</b>, all crop left/right values are "
"ignored."
msgstr ""
"Obreže podatke z leve strani grafa (dejansko približanje). <br>\n"
"    \tVrednost se razlaga kot odstotek skupne ali absolutne vrednosti, "
"odvisno od crop_mode_h. V odstotnem načinu vrednosti niso omejene na 0-100, "
"da se omogoči »pomanjšanje« (tj. obrezovanje -50 levo bo dodalo dodatno "
"polovico skupne vodoravne razdalje). Vrednosti nad 100 (v načinu %) dejansko "
"ne bodo prikazale ničesar. Če je <em>Vrsta grafa</em> nastavljena na "
"<b>Merilnik hitrosti</b>, se vse vrednosti obrezovanja levo/desno prezrejo."

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:66
#, kde-format
msgid "Crop right"
msgstr "Obreži desno"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:67
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Same as <em>Crop left</em> but for the right side, and percentage type is "
"interpreted as an inverse percentage (ie: 100 = do not crop anything). "
"Values under 0 will effectively not display anything."
msgstr ""
"Enako kot <em>Obreži levo</em>, vendar za desno stran, in vrsta odstotka se "
"tolmači kot obratni odstotek (tj.: 100 = ne obreži ničesar). Vrednosti pod 0 "
"dejansko ne prikaže ničesar."

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:70
#, kde-format
msgid "Crop mode vertical"
msgstr "Navpični način obrezovanja"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:77
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Decides how to interpret the <em>Crop bottom</em> and <em>Crop top</em> "
"values.<br/>\n"
"    \tWith an absolute value, it can zoom in to between 100 and 150m of "
"altitude to show\n"
"small changes in altitude between those 2 values better.<br/>\n"
"Note: for the vertical type, absolute values are latitude degrees (for the "
"location\n"
"source type) and altitude, heart rate, speed for the others interpreted as "
"the <em>Legend unit</em>\n"
"type where applicable (ie: a value of 10 for altitude will be considered "
"meters by default\n"
"but if changing <em>Legend unit</em> to feet it will mean 10 feet)."
msgstr ""
"Določa, kako tolmačiti vrednosti <em>Obreži na dnu</em> in <em>Obreži na "
"vrhu</em>.<br/>\n"
"    \tZ absolutno vrednostjo lahko poveča med 100 in 150 m nadmorske višine, "
"da bolje prikaže\n"
"majhne spremembe nadmorske višine med tema dvema vrednostma.<br/>\n"
"Opomba: za navpično vrsto se absolutne vrednosti stopinje zemljepisne širine "
"(za lokacijo\n"
"vrsta vira) in nadm. višina, srčni utrip, hitrost za druge tolmačijo kot "
"vrsta<em>enota Legende</em>,\n"
"kadar je to primerno (tj. vrednost 10 za nadmorsko višino se privzeto šteje "
"za metre,\n"
"če pa spremenite <em>enoto Legende</em> v čevlje, bo to pomenilo 10 čevljev)."

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:81
#, kde-format
msgid "Crop bottom"
msgstr "Obreži na dnu"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:83
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"Crops data from the bottom side of the graph (effectively zooming in). <br>\n"
"    \tThe value is interpreted either as a percentage of total or an "
"absolute value depending on crop_mode_v. In percentage mode the values are "
"not restricted to 0-100 to allow for \"zoom out\" behaviour (ie: cropping "
"-50 bot will add an extra half of the total vertical distance to the "
"bottom). Values over 100 (in % mode) will effectively not display anything. "
"If <em>Graph type</em> is <b>Speedometer</b>, this will set the minimum "
"needle position which will clamp all values that are lower."
msgstr ""
"Obreže podatke od spodnje strani grafa (dejansko približanje). <br>\n"
"    \tVrednost se razlaga kot odstotek skupne ali absolutne vrednosti, "
"odvisno od crop_mode_v. V odstotnem načinu vrednosti niso omejene na 0-100, "
"da se omogoči »pomanjšanje« (npr.: obrezovanje -50 bot bo dodalo dodatno "
"polovico skupne navpične razdalje do dna). Vrednosti nad 100 (v načinu %) "
"dejansko ne bodo prikazale ničesar. Če je <em>vrsta grafa</em> <b>Merilnik "
"hitrosti</b>, bo to nastavilo najmanjši položaj igle, ki bo pridržal vse "
"vrednosti, ki so nižje."

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:86
#, kde-format
msgid "Crop top"
msgstr "Obreži na vrhu"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:88
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Same as <em>Crop bottom</em> but for the top side, and percentage type is "
"interpreted as an inverse percentage (ie: 100 = do not crop anything).<br>\n"
"    \tValues under 0 will effectively not display anything."
msgstr ""
"Enako kot <em>Obreži na dnu</em>, vendar za vrhnjo stran, in odstotkovna "
"vrsta se razlaga kot obratni odstotek (tj.: 100 = ne obreži ničesar).<br>\n"
"    \tVrednosti pod 0 dejansko ne bodo prikazale ničesar."

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:91
#, kde-format
msgid "Graph color style"
msgstr "Barvni slog grafa"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:92
#, kde-format
msgid "See the documentation about the various styles available"
msgstr "Oglejte si dokumentacijo o različnih slogih, ki so na voljo"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:93
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"One color,Two colors,Solid past - thin future,Solid future - thin past,"
"Vertical gradient,Horizontal gradient,Color by duration,Color by altitude,"
"Color by heart rate,Color by Speed,Color by Speed (max 100km/h),Color by "
"grade (max 90 degrees),Color by grade (max 20 degrees)"
msgstr ""
"Ena barva,Dve barvi,Trdna preteklost - tanka prihodnost,Trdna prihodnost - "
"tanka preteklost,Navpični preliv,Vodoravni preliv,Barva po trajanju,Barva po "
"nadmorski višini,Barva po srčnem utripu,Varva po hitrosti,Barva po hitrosti "
"(največ 100 km/h),Barva po stopnji (največ 90 stopinj),Barva po stopnji "
"(največ 20 stopinj)"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:97
#, kde-format
msgid "Sets the color #1 for the graph line"
msgstr "Nastavi barvo #1 za črto grafa"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:101
#, kde-format
msgid "Sets the color #2 for the graph line"
msgstr "Nastavi barvo #2 za črto grafa"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:105
#, kde-format
msgid "Sets the color #3 for the graph line"
msgstr "Nastavi barvo #3 za črto grafa"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:109
#, kde-format
msgid "Sets the color #4 for the graph line"
msgstr "Nastavi barvo #4 za črto grafa"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:113
#, kde-format
msgid "Sets the color #5 for the graph line"
msgstr "Nastavi barvo #5 za črto grafa"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:116
#, kde-format
msgid "Show Now dot"
msgstr "Pokaži piko »zdaj«"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:118
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Enable it to draw a disc at the current location/time over the graph line."
"<br>\n"
"    \tIf graph type is speedometer, this affects the needle."
msgstr ""
"Omogočite, da nariše krog na trenutni lokaciji/času prek črte grafa.<br>\n"
"    \tČe je vrsta grafa merilnik hitrosti, to vpliva na iglo."

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:121
#, kde-format
msgid "Now dot color"
msgstr "Barva pike »zdaj«"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:122
#, kde-format
msgid "Sets the color for the Now dot"
msgstr "Nastavi barvo za piko »Zdaj«"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:125
#, kde-format
msgid "Show Now text"
msgstr "Pokaži besedilo »Zdaj«"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:127
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Enable it to draw the current value in big white bold letters on the bottom "
"right side of the rect.<br>\n"
"    \tThe <em>Legend unit</em> value will be appended at the end and it will "
"be used as the current unit (if a valid unit is found ie: kilometers if \"km"
"\" is found anywhere in the <em>Legend unit</em> string)."
msgstr ""
"Omogočite, da nariše trenutno vrednost v velikih belih krepkih črkah na "
"desni spodnji strani pravokotnika.<br>\n"
"    \tVrednost <em>enote legende</em> bo dodana na koncu in bo uporabljena "
"kot trenutna enota (če je najdena veljavna enota, tj.: kilometri, če je »km« "
"najden kjerkoli v nizu <em>enote legende</em> )."

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:131
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Rotate the entire graph rectangle. For speedometer type the text stays "
"horizontal."
msgstr ""
"Zasukajte celoten pravokotnik grafa. Pri vrsti merilnika hitrosti besedilo "
"ostane vodoravno."

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:134
#, kde-format
msgid "Line Thickness (px)"
msgstr "Debelina črte (sl. točke)"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:135
#, kde-format
msgid "Sets the thickness of the line graph in pixels."
msgstr "Nastavi debelino črtnega grafa v slikovnih točkah."

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:138
#, kde-format
msgid "Draw legend"
msgstr "Nariši legendo"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:140
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"If enabled it will draw 5 horizontal (and vertical for map type) <br>\n"
"    \tlines with small values each corresponding to the current data source "
"value at 0%, 25%, 50%, 75% and 100% of current graph shown, affected by the "
"<em>Legend unit</em> type if applicable, and with the string appended to the "
"value. For speedometer type this shows division values (but without "
"appending unit)."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočeno, nariše pet vodoravnih (in navpičnih za vrsto zemljevida) "
"<br>\n"
"    \\črt z majhnimi vrednostmi, od katerih vsaka ustreza trenutni vrednosti "
"vira podatkov pri 0 %, 25 %, 50 %, 75 % in 100 % trenutnega grafa, na "
"katerega vpliva vrsta <em>enot legende</em> , če je primerno, in z nizom, "
"dodanim vrednosti. Za vrsto merilnika hitrosti to prikazuje vrednosti "
"deljenja (vendar brez dodajanja enote)."

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:143
#, kde-format
msgid "Legend unit"
msgstr "Enota legende"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:145
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Sets the unit to be used for displaying values of type altitude and speed."
"<br>\n"
"        Default is meters and km/h respectively. The unit is matched "
"anywhere in the string so extra spaces can be used to tweak displaying."
msgstr ""
"Določa enoto, ki se uporablja za prikaz vrednosti vrste višine in hitrosti."
"<br>\n"
"    \tPrivzeto so to metri oziroma km/h. Enota se ujema kjerkoli v nizu, "
"tako da se lahko uporabijo dodatni presledki za prilagoditev prikaza."

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:146
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"m,meter,km,kilometer,mi,mile,ft,feet,nm,nautical,ms,m/s,meter per sec,km,km/"
"h,kilometer per hr,mi,mi/h,mile per hr,ft,ft/s,feet per sec,kn,nm/h,knots,"
"mmin,m/min,ftmin,ft/min"
msgstr ""
"m,meter,km,kilometer,mi,milja,ft,čevlji,nm,navtičnih,ms,m/s,meter na sekundo,"
"km,km/h,kilometer na uro,mi,mi/h,milja na uro,ft,ft/s,čevljev na sekundo,kn,"
"nm/h,vozli,mmin,m/min,ftmin,ft/min"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:149
#, kde-format
msgid "Show dots only"
msgstr "Pokaži samo pike"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:151
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, the graph will be drawn using individual dots instead of lines."
"<br>\n"
"    \tThis will effectively show the individual data points as affected by "
"smoothing (ie: for location data it will display each GPS fix if smoothing "
"is 1) and can either be used as a cool effect when zoomed in enough or to "
"debug unexpected line jumps."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočeno, bo grafikon narisan s posameznimi pikami namesto črtami."
"<br>\n"
"    \tTo bo učinkovito prikazalo posamezne podatkovne točke, na katere "
"vpliva glajenje (tj. za podatke o lokaciji bo prikazan vsak popravek GPS, če "
"je glajenje 1) in se lahko uporabi kot lep učinek, ko je dovolj približan, "
"ali za odpravljanje nepričakovanih skokov črt."

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:154
#, kde-format
msgid "Graph rectangle"
msgstr "Pravokotnik grafa"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:156
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"Defines the rectangle that the graph should be drawn in.<br>\n"
"        Format is: \"X Y W H\". X, Y, W, H are assumed to be pixel units "
"unless they have the suffix '%'."
msgstr ""
"Določa pravokotnik, v katerem naj bo narisan graf.<br>\n"
"    \tOblika je: »X Y Š V«. X, Y, Š, V so praviloma v enotah slikovnih točk, "
"razen če imajo pripono »%«."

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:159
#, kde-format
msgid "Background image"
msgstr "Slika ozadja"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:161
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"If a valid image file is selected, it will be used as a background for the "
"rectangle area.<br>\n"
"      \tPaths starting with the \"!\" character are ignored. TIP: use a map "
"image to add context to the GPS track."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrana veljavna slikovna datoteka, bo uporabljena kot ozadje za "
"pravokotno področje.<br>\n"
"    \tPoti, ki se začnejo z znakom »!«, so prezrte. NASVET: uporabite sliko "
"zemljevida, da dodate kontekst sledi GPS."

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:164
#, kde-format
msgid "Background scale"
msgstr "Merilo ozadja"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:166
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Scale the background image (relative to center) to match it to the above GPS "
"track.<br>\n"
"    \tValues smaller than 100 zoom into the image, values larger than 100 "
"zoom out. 0 hides it."
msgstr ""
"Spremeni merilo slike ozadja (relativno na središče), da se ujema z zgornjo "
"stezo GPS.<br>\n"
"    \tVrednosti, manjše od 100, povečajo sliko, vrednosti, večje od 100, jo "
"pomanjšajo. 0 jo skrije."

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:169 src/titler/titlewidget.cpp:385
#, kde-format
msgid "Background opacity"
msgstr "Prekrivnost ozadja"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:170
#, kde-format
msgid "Sets the opacity for the background image"
msgstr "Nastavi prekrivnost slike ozadja"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:173
#, kde-format
msgid "GPS start time"
msgstr "Začetni čas GPS"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:174
#, kde-format
msgid "Date and time of the first valid GPS point."
msgstr "Datum in čas prve veljavne točke GPS."

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:177
#, kde-format
msgid "Video start time"
msgstr "Čas začetka videoposnetka"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:178
#, kde-format
msgid "Date and time of the video file."
msgstr "Datum in čas videodatoteke."

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:181
#, kde-format
msgid "Auto offset start"
msgstr "Začetek samodejnega zamika"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:182
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Provides a helper offset to guarantee start of video file syncs with the "
"start of GPS file. Correctly sets the offset if video file and GPS recording "
"was started at the same time."
msgstr ""
"Zagotavlja pomožni zamik, ki zagotavlja začetek sinhronizacije video datotek "
"z začetkom datoteke GPS. Pravilno nastavi zamik, če sta se videodatoteka in "
"posnetek GPS začela hkrati."

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:185
#, kde-format
msgid "Auto offset now"
msgstr "Samodejni zamik zdaj"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:186
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Provides a helper offset to sync the first GPS point to current video time "
"(it is updated every second). Correctly sets the offset if your video record "
"the moment GPS starts."
msgstr ""
"Zagotavlja pomožni zamik za sinhronizacijo prve točke GPS s trenutnim časom "
"videa (posodablja se vsako sekundo). Pravilno nastavi uamik, če "
"videoposnetek posname trenutek, ko se zažene GPS."

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:189
#, kde-format
msgid "Map hint"
msgstr "Namig na zemljevidu"

#: data/effects/gpsgraphic.xml:190
#, kde-format
msgid "Returns the middle latitude and longitude coordinates of the gps file."
msgstr "Vrne koordinate srednje zemljepisne širine in dolžine datoteke gps."

