#: data/effects/rboctaveshift.xml:5 data/effects/rbpitchscale.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid "Adjust the audio pitch using the Rubberband library."
msgstr "Prilagodite višino tona s pomočjo knjižnice Rubberband."

#: data/effects/rboctaveshift.xml:8
#, kde-format
msgid "Octave Shift"
msgstr "Zamik za oktavo"

#: data/effects/rboctaveshift.xml:9
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The octave shift. This is the octave shift of the source frequency. For "
"example, a shift of +1 would double the frequency; -1 would halve the "
"frequency and 0 would leave the pitch unaffected. To put this in frequency "
"terms, a frequency shift f (where f greater than one for upwards shift and "
"less than one for downwards) is: o = log(f) / log(2). Ignored if pitchscale "
"is set."
msgstr ""
"Zamik za oktavo. To je oktavni zamik izvorne frekvence. Primer: zamik "
"+1podvoji frekvenco; -1 prepolovi frekvenco in 0 pusti višino tona "
"nespremenjeno. Če to izrazimo v frekvenčnih pojmih, kjer je frekvenčni "
"premik f (kjer je f večji od ena za zamik navzgor in manjši od ena za zamik "
"navzdol), je to: o = log(f) / log(2). Prezrto, če je nastavljeno "
"spreminjanje višine tona."

#: data/effects/rboctaveshift.xml:12 data/effects/rbpitchscale.xml:12
#, kde-format
msgid "Stretch"
msgstr "Raztegni"

#: data/effects/rboctaveshift.xml:13 data/effects/rbpitchscale.xml:13
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Stretch the audio to fill the requested samples. This option will have no "
"effect if the requested sample size is the same as the received sample size."
msgstr ""
"Raztegnite zvok, da zapolnite potrebne vzorce. Ta možnost ne bo imela "
"učinka, če je zahtevana velikost vzorca enaka prejeti velikosti vzorca."

#: data/effects/rboctaveshift.xml:16 data/effects/rbpitchscale.xml:16
#, kde-format
msgid "Latency"
msgstr "Latenca"

#: data/effects/rboctaveshift.xml:17 data/effects/rbpitchscale.xml:17
#, kde-format
msgid "The amount of delay for each sample from the input to the output."
msgstr "Količina zakasnitve za vsak vzorec od vhoda do izhoda."

#: data/effects/rbpitchscale.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgid "Rubberband Pitch Scale"
msgstr "Spreminjanje višine tona Rubberband"

#: data/effects/rbpitchscale.xml:8
#, kde-format
msgid "Pitch Scale"
msgstr "Spreminjanje višine tona"

#: data/effects/rbpitchscale.xml:9
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The pitch scaling ratio. This is the ratio of target frequency to source "
"frequency. For example, a ratio of 2.0 would shift up by one octave; 0.5 "
"down by one octave; or 1.0 leave the pitch unaffected. To put this in "
"musical terms, a pitch scaling ratio corresponding to a shift of o octaves "
"(where o is positive for an upwards shift and negative for downwards) is: f "
"= pow(2.0, o). Overrides octaveshift."
msgstr ""
"Razmerje spreminjanja višine tona. To je razmerje med ciljno frekvenco in "
"izvorno frekvenco. Primer: razmerje 2,0 zamakne frekvenco navzgor za eno "
"oktavo; 0,5 navzdol za eno oktavo; 1,0 pusti višino tona nespremenjeno. Če "
"to izrazimo v glasbenem jeziku: razmerje spremembe višine tona za zamik za o "
"oktav (kjer je o pozitiven za zamik navzgor in negativen za zamik navzdol) "
"je: f = pow(2.0, o). Preglasi nastavitev zamika oktave."

