msgid ""
"This performs the PSNR and SSIM video quality measurements by comparing the "
"B frames to the reference frame A. It outputs the numbers to stdout in space-"
"delimited format for easy by another tool. The bottom half of the B frame is "
"placed below the top half of the A frame for visual comparison."
